- The street ends at Taksim Square, which is described as the heart of modern Istanbul, suggesting a prestigious location.
- The presence of luxurious five-star hotels along the street indicates a high level of luxury.
- The street is lined with the glass-fronted Ataturk Cultural Centre, also known as the Opera House, which adds to the luxurious ambiance.
- The combination of high-end hotels and cultural landmarks suggests an upscale environment.